the "NewsHour."

08:47.494 --> 08:49.295 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BENJAMIN GINSBERG, Former Mitt
Romney General
Counsel: Thank you. Thank you
for having me.

08:49.396 --> 08:52.732 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
