09:15.755 --> 09:19.125 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, what's
happening now is
that, after the number of
delegates is chosen

09:19.225 --> 09:24.531 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
