Cleveland.

09:43.483 --> 09:49.622 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And how are those
decisions
made? A lot of it is personal
relationships,

09:49.722 --> 09:54.661 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
