who is already
in the party hierarchy in a
particular state.

09:54.761 --> 09:56.463 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BENJAMIN GINSBERG: Yes.

09:56.563 --> 09:59.399 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
