36:01.359 --> 36:03.361 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON (D),
Presidential Candidate:
Finally, fathers will be able to
say to their

36:03.461 --> 36:06.464 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
