potential Smith
run.

37:05.290 --> 37:07.392 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN F. KENNEDY, President of
the United States:
If I were a Republican
candidate, I would

37:07.492 --> 37:10.895 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
