37:15.166 --> 37:20.205 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Smith's bid for
the 1964 Republican
nomination was unsuccessful, but
her candidacy

37:20.305 --> 37:25.510 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
