37:29.013 --> 37:32.817 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MARGARET CHASE SMITH,
Presidential Candidate:
Women before me pioneered and
smoothed the

37:32.917 --> 37:40.959 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
way for me to be the first women
