38:19.130 --> 38:20.932 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(APPLAUSE)

38:21.032 --> 38:26.971 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHIRLEY CHISHOLM: I am not the
candidate of
the women's movement of this
country, although

38:27.071 --> 38:30.842 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
