49:58.729 --> 50:02.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that you're sometimes left
unsure what those
statements even mean.

50:02.533 --> 50:07.671 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I used to work for a politician
as a speechwriter,
and I confess I came up with
fair amount of

50:07.771 --> 50:13.310 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
